Quote:  Can't the civilian police do something with that fiend who accosts  the lately returned soldier ... then he tries the beer-bite with `How is it for a couple of bob?' Inquiry shows that some of these `Beer-biters' are ordinary `civvy' loafers ... The R.S.A. has denounced the `beer-biter'.
